title: Device phone number does not match my actual number.
content:
Hi, when I go Settings  > About Device > Phone number,  I can see some number which is definitely not my number. 
When I check Settings > Google> Device phone number, I see 'No number available'. 
Besides this everything works, I can call and receiver can see my actual number.
Any idea what could be problem? Is there a chance that my phone is hacked?
Thanks
